## 8. COMMIT MESAJ FORMATI

```
<type>(<scope>): <description>

[optional body]

[optional footer]
```

Types:
- `feat`: Yeni özellik
- `fix`: Bug fix
- `refactor`: Kod iyileştirme
- `docs`: Dokümantasyon
- `style`: Formatting
- `perf`: Performans
- `test`: Test ekleme

Örnekler:
```
feat(analytics): add PnL cumulative chart
fix(hud): resolve modal z-index issue
refactor(3d): optimize Habitat render loop
```

